title: WINCHESTER LARGE STUDIO~ UTILITIES INC~Pool~Parking~Walk to center~
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 2775766', 'Rent: $1,695 / Month', 'Beds: 0', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 09/15/2022', 'Pet: No Pets', 'Rent Includes:: Electricity, Heat, Hot Water', 'Parking:: off-street parking', 'Large, nicely renovated studio located on the Terrace level of an apartment community in Winchester.', ' Located in the heart of Winchester, walk to trains and center.', 'Condo offers a nicely updated eat-in kitchen,  Berber carpet, and tiled bath.', '  Living area and bedroom area have a half wall; no door.', 'Heat, hot water, electricity and parking included in one low price!!', ' NO Pets!!', 'Walk out to your own private patio overlooking a beautiful pond.', 'Pool, barbecue area, and parking available.', 'Coin-Op laundry in the basement.', 'First, security, half month fee.', 'Last month can be broken up first 4-6 months.', '1 car parking 2nd spot additional $600 for year', 'Terms:  2 year lease preferred.', 'Good credit, references a must!', 'email or call today to schedule a showing.', '~~Please Email or Call for a showing today!~~', '~Offering personal or virtual tours~', 'Surrounded by lush green gardens, walking paths, waterways & duck ponds...a hidden gem on the back side of the building right off Main Street in Winchester.', 'Enjoy summer days by the in-ground pool, take advantage of the very social in-building laundry facilities, ample parking, storage unit, on-site management and minutes to Winchester center, shops, train to Boston', 'FEATURES', 'A/C', 'Balcony', 'Carpet', 'Central Air', 'Dishwasher', 'Elevator', 'End Unit', 'Laundry in Building', 'Modern Bath', 'Modern Kitchen', 'newly renovated', 'On-Site Super', 'Storage', 'Swimming Pool', 'Walk-In Closet', 'GMRE is an "Equal Housing Opportunity" Real Estate Agency.', ' It is against the Law of MA to refuse to rent to Families with Children or to otherwise discriminate in housing rentals.']
